<paragraph blockId="0.[1225,2108,777,1366]" pageId="0" pageNumber="400">• Open sclerophyll forests and woodlands with acceptable eucalypt food trees.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1225,2108,777,1366]" box="[1226,1673,1290,1319]" pageId="0" pageNumber="400">• 1 genus, 1 species, 1 taxon.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1225,2108,777,1366]" box="[1227,1996,1326,1359]" pageId="0" pageNumber="400">• No species threatened; none Extinct since 1600.</paragraph>
